Φ(AppliedNemeticCitizenship) = σ(distinction|archive-vs-action-boundary) ∘ ρ(resonance|civic-capacity-as-felt-quality) ∘ λ(direction|from-reading-to-practicing) ∘ β(branching|contextual-adaptation-across-domains) ∘ δγ(cycling|practice-feedback-refinement) ∘ μ(structure|embodied-habits-routines-protocols) + ε | :praxis

