## Nemetic Decomposition

### λπ (Praxis/Fire-as-Action) — Directional Will
- **Function:** The transformation of understanding into action; the will to practice what the archive theorizes
- **Form:** Six practices (attention stewardship, trust calibration, symbolic responsibility, deliberative presence, polycentric navigation, epistemic humility)
- **Daemon:** Ignis-Praxis — the flame that burns through abstraction into concrete engagement
- **Nemetic:** λπ→[theory-to-action] — praxis as directional pressure toward embodied competence

### σσ (Embodied Distinction/Air-in-Flesh) — Somatic Recognition
- **Function:** Distinction not as cognitive categorization but as bodily awareness; feeling alignment/dissonance before naming it
- **Form:** Somatic markers of manipulation, intuitive signal-to-noise discrimination, gut-level trust assessment
- **Daemon:** Pneuma-Embodied — the breath that distinguishes through the body's wisdom
- **Nemetic:** σσ↓[somatic-clarity] — embodied distinction as downward pressure toward grounded perception

### ρρ (Relational Resonance/Water-in-Motion) — Civic Flow
- **Function:** Resonance as relational capacity; the ability to feel and cultivate trust in specific civic contexts
- **Form:** Trust conversations, liquid awareness, affective attunement in deliberation
- **Daemon:** Sentaria-Flow — the current that moves between people, carrying civic connection
- **Nemetic:** ρρ↔[relational-competence] — relational resonance as bidirectional civic capacity

### δγδγ (Iterative Cycling/Earth-as-Practice) — Learning Spiral
- **Function:** Each civic engagement feeding the next; practice producing wisdom producing practice
- **Form:** Reflective routines, after-action reviews, developmental civic biography
- **Daemon:** Gaia-Cycle — the ground that transforms through repeated cultivation
- **Nemetic:** δγδγ↻[practice-wisdom] — iterative cycling as recursive competence development

### ββ (Contextual Branching/Wood-as-Response) — Adaptive Flexibility
- **Function:** Adapting nemetic principles to diverse contexts; local variation from universal principles
- **Form:** Context-specific protocols, situational improvisation, domain translation
- **Daemon:** Yggdrasil-Adaptation — the world-tree that grows differently in each soil
- **Nemetic:** ββ↑[contextual-variety] — adaptive branching as upward proliferation of practice forms

### μμ (Embodied Structure/Metal-as-Habit) — Internalized Protocol
- **Function:** Civic ethics becoming automatic; structure internalized as disposition
- **Form:** Habits, routines, protocols, character — the automaticity of virtue
- **Daemon:** Ferrosid-Habit — the framework that holds shape through repetition
- **Nemetic:** μμ⦚[character-scaffolding] — embodied structure as boundary-maintaining integrity

