## Nemetic String Variants

### Compressed Form
```
Φ(D030) = λπ∘σσ∘ρρ∘δγδγ∘ββ∘μμ + ε | :praxis
```

### Elemental Weight Distribution (Praxis-Level)
```
λπ: 0.22 (praxis-leading)
σσ: 0.18 (embodied-distinction-secondary)
ρρ: 0.17 (relational-resonance-tertiary)
δγδγ: 0.16 (iterative-cycling-quaternary)
ββ: 0.14 (contextual-branching-quinary)
μμ: 0.13 (embodied-structure-senary)
```

### Process Flow
```
Archive[Input] 
  → λπ[Praxis Intention: will to act] 
  → σσ[Somatic Recognition: feel the situation] 
  → ρρ[Relational Resonance: connect with others] 
  → ββ[Contextual Adaptation: respond appropriately] 
  → μμ[Embodied Structure: act from habit/virtue] 
  → δγδγ[Reflective Cycling: learn from action] 
  → Competence[Output] 
  → λπ[New Intention: continue the practice]
```

### Entanglement Markers
- **π** (praxis): Action suffix on operators — theory becoming practice
- **σσ** (doubled): Embodied distinction — distinction felt in the body
- **ρρ** (doubled): Relational resonance — resonance between persons
- **δγδγ** (doubled): Iterative cycling — practice as recursive learning
- **ββ** (doubled): Contextual branching — adaptation to specific situations
- **μμ** (doubled): Embodied structure — habits and character

